    <string name="gui_generator_intro"><![CDATA[ni li ilo pali pi musi tawa lon Juggling Lab. ni li alasa e musi tawa kepeken
sitelen siteswap. o lukin e lipu https://jugglinglab.org tan sona ali. musi
tawa wan lon tenpo li nasin majuna.

nasin kepeken:   gen <nanpa ijo> <pana suli> <tenpo musi> [nasin ante]

nasin ante li ni:
  -n             o lukin e nanpa musi
  -no            o sitelen e nanpa taso
  -se            o len e pini e open pi musi sewi

  -x <regex> ..  o weka e sitelen ni
  -i <regex> ..  o pana e sitelen ni
  -lame          o weka e '11' lon nasin tawa tu

  -g             musi anpa taso
  -ng            musi sewi taso
  -f             lipu musi ali
  -prime         musi suli taso
  -rot           o lukin e musi sike ali (sama 645 en 564)

  -m <nanpa>     pana mute kepeken nanpa ni
  -mf            o ken e kama jo sama (musi squeeze)
  -mc            o weka e pana kulupu (sama [33])
  -mt            o wile e pana mute wan kepeken awen ala

  -s             o alasa e musi tawa wan

  -j <nanpa>     o pana e nanpa jan musi
  -cp            o lukin e musi wan taso pi jan mute
  -sym           o lukin e musi samajala pi jan musi
  -group         o kulupu e pana kepeken jan musi
  -d <nanpa>     tenpo awen pi pana jan (o lukin e lipu)
  -l <nanpa>     nanpa jan sewi pi pana jan (kepeken -d)
  -jp            o lukin e ante ali pi jan musi

Ejemplos:
  gen 5 7 5
  gen 5 7 1-5 -x 2 3
  gen 5 7 - -prime -n
  gen 4 - 3 -f -rot -no
  gen 4 6 6 -s -g
  gen 5 6 4 -m 2 -g -mt
  gen 6 4 2 -j 2 -g -jp -m 2 -d 1 -l 1]]></string>
    <string name="gui_transitioner_intro"><![CDATA[ni li ilo alasa pi tawa ante lon Juggling Lab. ni li alasa e tawa ante lon
musi tawa tu.

nasin ante li mute. ilo li pali e nasin mute tan A tawa B.

nasin kepeken:   trans <musi A> <musi B> [-nasin ante]

nasin ante li ni:
  -m <nanpa>     pana mute kepeken nanpa ni
  -mf            o ken e kama jo sama (musi squeeze)
  -mc            o weka e pana kulupu (sama [33])
  -limits        o weka e pini tenpo en nanpa musi

Ejemplos:
  trans 5 771
  trans 5 771 -m 2
  trans 645 '(6x,4)*'
  trans '<33|22>' '<55|00>']]></string>
    <string name="gui_cli_help1"><![CDATA[ilo linja pi ilo Juggling Lab. nasin ni li lon:

   jlab start
      o open e ilo.

   jlab open <lipu1.jml> <lipu2.jml> ...
      o open e lipu JML ni.

   jlab anim <musi> [-prefs <nasin>]
      o open e lupa lukin pi musi tawa.

   jlab gen <nasin_gen> [-out <nasin_lipu>]
      o pali e ilo alasa pi musi tawa.

   jlab trans <musi A> <musi B> [-nasin] [-out <nasin_lipu>]
      o alasa e tawa ante tan A tawa B.

   jlab togif <musi> [-prefs <nasin>] -out <nasin_lipu>
      o awen e musi tawa lon lipu GIF.

   jlab tojml <musi> [-out <nasin_lipu>]
      o ante e musi tawa sitelen JML XML.

   jlab verify [-tojml] <lipu1.jml> <lipu2.jml> ... [-out <nasin_lipu>]
      o lukin e pona pi lipu JML ni.]]></string>
    <string name="gui_cli_help2"><![CDATA[Ejemplos:
   jlab anim '(6x,4)*'
   jlab togif 'pattern=3;dwell=1.0;bps=4.0;hands=(-30)(2.5).(30)(-2.5).(-30)(0).' -out mills.gif
   jlab anim -jml musi_pona_mi.jml
   jlab anim 771 -prefs 'stereo=true;width=800;height=600'
   jlab anim 5B -prefs 'bouncesound=true'
   jlab gen 5 7 5
   jlab trans 5 771]]></string>
